---
title: Tater-Topped Pot Pie with Chicken, Mushrooms, and Peas
description: Chicken pot pie is an oldie and a goodie. Who can resist a filling of meat and veg in gravy under a golden crust? But making it with the traditional pie dough can be time-consuming, which is why we’re introducing a quick fix that makes it do-able any night of the week. By using sliced Yukon potatoes, you can simply lay the spuds on top, pop the pie in the oven, then broil ’til it’s browned and gorgeous.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/w09-r01-f58c6b24.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/w09-r01-ebd3298c.pdf
cuisine: North America
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/tater-topped-pot-pie-58821e8a4348d25681058572
time required: 45 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 680 kcal
  fat: 24 g
